🔐 RBAC Implementation – POS SaaS Backend
=========================================
📌 Overview
------------

This project implements Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) using:

Spring Security

JWT Authentication

Method-level security (@PreAuthorize)

Multi-tenant isolation

Access to APIs is controlled based on the authenticated user’s role.

🛡️ Security Configuration
-------------------------

Stateless authentication (SessionCreationPolicy.STATELESS)

JWT required for all protected endpoints

Method-level security enabled:

@EnableMethodSecurity


Public endpoints:

/api/auth/**
/api/test/**
/swagger-ui/**
/v3/api-docs/**


All other endpoints require authentication.

👤 Roles Defined
----------------
public enum Role {
    ROLE_SUPER_ADMIN,
    ROLE_STORE_ADMIN,
    ROLE_BRANCH_MANAGER,
    ROLE_CASHIER,
    ROLE_VIEWER
}


Each user has exactly one role stored as an ENUM.

🔄 Role → Authority Mapping
----------------------------

User roles are converted to Spring Security authorities:

new SimpleGrantedAuthority(user.getRole().name())


Example:

ROLE_STORE_ADMIN


Used in controllers with:

@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ROLE_STORE_ADMIN')")

📋 Role-Permission Matrix
------------------------
🛒 Product APIs
---------------
Endpoint	Method	Access
/api/products	POST	STORE_ADMIN
/api/products	GET	STORE_ADMIN, CASHIER, BRANCH_MANAGER, VIEWER

👥 User APIs
------------
Endpoint	Method	Access
/api/users	GET	STORE_ADMIN
/api/users	POST	STORE_ADMIN

🔐 Authorization Flow
---------------------
Client logs in → receives JWT.

JWT sent in header:

Authorization: Bearer <token>


JWT filter validates token.

Spring checks required role using @PreAuthorize.

Access granted or denied.

🏢 Multi-Tenancy
----------------
Each request must include:

X-Tenant-ID: <tenant-id>


Tenant isolation is handled using TenantContext and filters.

❌ Access Control Behavior
--------------------------
Scenario	Result
No token	401 / 403
Invalid token	403
Insufficient role	403
Valid role	200 / 201

✅ Summary
----------

Stateless JWT authentication

Method-level RBAC

Tenant isolation

Role-permission matrix documented

Integration tests verify access control